title: Russia has evidence Syria chemical attack fabricated - Russian FM
text:
Russia has evidence Syria chemical attack fabricated - Russian FM 7:10pm IST - 00:59 
Russia’s foreign minister says Moscow has “undeniable evidence” that the attack in Douma was staged by a “certain nation” in the front row of what he called a Russphobic campaign. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
